{"tid":2403125,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國提升對華旅警｜德國外交部警告赴中國國民：旅客或被強制醫院隔離數周每日抽血","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:41:32.000Z","uid":239336,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a780f50fa38c2ec0645f7c89e4a335e1abbd15da","tid":2403125,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"德國提升對中國的旅遊警示，警告包括武漢肺炎康復者在內的旅客抵達中國時，可被當局要求在醫院隔離數周，甚或面對侵入性醫學檢查。<br />\n<br />\n德國外交部指中國的入境防疫措施適用於武肺康復者、被驗出含抗體人士、或曾與確診者乘坐同一班航機的旅客，「中方採取的醫療措施是具侵入性，包括每日抽血化驗和電腦掃描」。而所有抵華旅客亦要依政府安排，在指定隔離地點包括醫院等強制隔離14天，同行人士如已年滿14歲，更有機會被安排與家人分開不同地點隔離。<br />\n<br />\n《南德意志報》報道，政府是有見兩名德國公民入境中國後被強制於醫院隔離多周，決定收緊對中國的旅遊警示。報道指兩人都是武肺康復者、體內有抗體，但仍被迫接受醫學檢查，德國外交部已就事件向中方提出抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210211/5ZIRIPQQ6RBWDHRXIW5KHVHO3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210211%2F5ZIRIPQQ6RBWDHRXIW5KHVHO3Q%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLKkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=213ba1e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210211%2F5ZIRIPQQ6RBWDHRXIW5KHVHO3Q%2F&h=88ec5f63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210211/5ZIRIPQQ6RBWDHRXIW5KHVHO3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"61d0835ff5a30935eba4a9124bb804e0af0ef598","tid":2403125,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:21:56.000Z","msg":"傳聞元首投胎到咗中國<br />\n<br />\n不過唔完整，係劣化版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WM41sWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWM41sWV.jpg&h=8b165592&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce42891bb648105da403208290c4f53c0a66ef12","tid":2403125,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"做實驗用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715718d2d12328b46e19a9b9b6681e7aced07693","tid":2403125,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,